{"tid":2247480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戀童燈極有可能退選","createTime":"2020-10-18T01:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T04:15:09.000Z","uid":374134,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"091774ff58d6dd3d807fcefc85b7fb4e2ea59c51","tid":2247480,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENpcEuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENpcEuF.jpg&h=17e64086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">美國大選進入倒數計時。圖為美國總統川普（左）和民主黨競選對手拜登（右）</span><br />\n距美大選前僅20天，民主黨總統候選人拜登的兒子杭特（Hunter Biden）「通烏門」事件再發酵！易經命理老師高煜霖從卦象來看，拜登極可能會慘敗，甚至搞不好會退選。<br />\n<br />\n川普針對拜登的兒子杭特與烏克蘭之間的利益糾葛，川普在推特表示，要拜登說清楚。高煜霖在臉書粉專「易經粉絲團」指出，「通烏門」事件恐是川普計畫性「養案」，來打擊對手的策略，選舉結果，<span class=\"gold\">拜登極可能會慘敗，嚴重者，選前搞不好他會退選</span>。<br />\n<br />\n高煜霖看卦象，從「小吉」判斷，噬辭「行人即便至，交關甚是強」，顯示事態恐越演越烈，讓國際的政府或團體，甚至美國本土，持續丟一些不利拜登的訊息。另一句「凡事皆和合，病者叩穹蒼」，顯示選前這10幾天，出現不利拜登的訊息，恐招招都能「一槍斃命」。<br />\n<br />\n高煜霖另從綜合加權指數分析，今年適逢美國人口普查年，選舉人票的劃分，很可能又是一項能操作的工具。在易經演繹換算下，如果順利投票，川普有機會在選舉人得票數，超越70%、甚至75%；如以2010年選舉人票有538票來看，大約376票至403票。<br />\n<br />\nLink:  <a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201017003013-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201017003013-260407&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=86a0dc80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201017003013-260407</a>"},{"pid":"05ff7b116f54370fe377e2915f6e64723c2356b2","tid":2247480,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3a5babce284e1b4bc915cc31fb6f33441e575aa","tid":2247480,"uid":11914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"唔會，拜登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d926421c7765781d6299ccff6d35e05045819a2c","tid":2247480,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"一退全個黨D醜聞不斷爆，只有一條路咋！"},{"pid":"87f274bee6af4cb69875e00691522bd1697fb4a7","tid":2247480,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d926421c7765781d6299ccff6d35e05045819a2c","tid":2247480,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"一退全個黨D醜聞不斷爆，只有一條路咋！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好用不推文"},{"pid":"d7621d3690f667700f898127a2edd37bd47f1034","tid":2247480,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:48:50.000Z","msg":"又一個神棍出嚟鳩嗡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20120225/J3M2SEQYVXGUPKHXF2CLZSURWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20120225%2FJ3M2SEQYVXGUPKHXF2CLZSURWE%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=09de2197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20120225%2FJ3M2SEQYVXGUPKHXF2CLZSURWE%2F&h=e945d4cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20120225/J3M2SEQYVXGUPKHXF2CLZSURWE/</a>"},{"pid":"b3f49faecaffc71ea1aeddadce1ab1c68b766b78","tid":2247480,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:09:21.000Z","msg":"陣前換帥? 兵家大忌也!!!<br />\n<br />\n點樣死都要衝左先<br />\n<br />\n輸左都無所謂........勇士不留頭.<br />\n敵將討伐DOCTOR LEE"},{"pid":"5241a617d99db99fc074fc30474b3882d442b876","tid":2247480,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"中共幾時滅"},{"pid":"25087a11553529f4c436206df402b30d7dccc39c","tid":2247480,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:15:09.000Z","msg":"明明拜燈今年行衰運，亥子丑三會忌神官星（子星），唔通真係俾佢嗰仔累死？"}],"pinned":{"pid":"87f274bee6af4cb69875e00691522bd1697fb4a7","tid":2247480,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18